name: The inner life of the morning coffee
description:
Another organisism drawing that started off as a loose idea, but ended with something very different. What does the morning coffee mean to you? To me, its the first creative explosion of the day. Its where the cranks and gears in my head start to move, and within the second cup I've already had loads of new ideas and odd thoughts.

Dark
Steaming
Thick and strong
Like the hand cranks an old combustion engine
and the gears move
Mornin' y'all, I'm good to go
